:

1. *Pukovniče* je bio nagrađen za hrabrost u ratu. (The colonel was awarded for bravery in war.)
2. Njegov otac bio je *pukovnik* u vojsci. (His father was a colonel in the army.)
3. *Pukovniče* je vodio svoje ljude u bitku. (The colonel led his people into battle.)
4. Njegov sin je postao *pukovnik* u vojsci. (His son became a colonel in the army.)
5. *Pukovniče* je bio uzoran zapovednik. (The colonel was an exemplary commander.)